title: Warcraft 3 ROC + TFT + online play
description:
The complete Warcraft3:Reign of Chaos, and Thr Frozen Throne with online play and singleplayer.
Note: the online multiplayer is not battle.net, it is a private server.

EDIT:They updated the private server to a new patch, follow the guidelines here http://sumurbatu-games.blogspot.com/2008/09/how-to-connect-on-eurobattlenet-new.html to connect to multiplayer.
